Mac Life USA July 2014 (Secure Your Stuff) 
English | 100 pages | HQ PDF | 101.69 Mb

Mac|Life is the leading independent magazine devoted to all things Apple. For over five years, Mac Life has helped both new and veteran users get more out of their iPhones, iPads, Macs, and more, with coverage that cuts through today's glut of apps and accessories to find what matters most. With a bright, clean design and casual tone, MacLife offers an easy and enjoyable way to keep up with the latest Apple trends and topics.
